<lb n="0744b07"/><head type="no">No. 798</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0744b08"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title><note n="0744003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛說〕－【宋】【元】【宮】</note><app n="0744003"><lem>佛說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>進學經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0744b09"/>
<lb n="0744b10"/><byline type="Translator">宋居士沮渠京聲譯</byline>
<lb n="0744b11"/><p>聞如是。一時佛遊舍衛祇樹之園須達精舍。
<lb n="0744b12"/>大賢眾千二百五十人。佛告諸比丘。有四雅
<lb n="0744b13"/>行。智者常遵。丈夫所修。達士&M010527;奉。不才愚夫
<lb n="0744b14"/>所不好樂。何等為四。孝事父母悅色養<note n="0744004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">足＝之【三】【宮】</note><note n="0744004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">足＝之【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0744004"><lem>足</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">之</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0744b15"/>守仁行慈終始不殺。惠施濟乏未曾&CB00385;逆。遭
<lb n="0744b16"/>值聖世捐榮履道。是四雅行。智者所遵。丈夫
<lb n="0744b17"/>所修。達士所奉。<note n="0744005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不才＝下才【宮】</note><app n="0744005"><lem>不才</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">下才</rdg></app>愚夫所不好樂。佛時
<lb n="0744b18"/>頌曰</p>
<lb n="0744b19"/><lg><l>智者稱孝</l><l>愍<note n="0744006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＝念【三】【宮】</note><note n="0744006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">命＝念【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0744006"><lem>命</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">念</rdg></app>慈活</l><l>放施普給</l>
<lb n="0744b20"/><l>超俗崇寂</l><l>如是正業</l><l>明士所習</l>
<lb n="0744b21"/><l>聖見已具</l><l>定<note n="0744007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">至＝天【宮】</note><app n="0744007"><lem>至</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">天</rdg></app>無為</l></lg>
<lb n="0744b22"/><p>佛告比丘。復有二法。若在閑宴。或處大眾。
<lb n="0744b23"/><note n="0744008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＝必【三】【宮】</note><note n="0744008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心＝必【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0744008"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">必</rdg></app>行莫懈。一者靜寂賢聖默定。二者博學講
<lb n="0744b24"/>論邃義。又有二施。<note n="0744009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飲食＝飯食【三】【宮】</note><note n="0744009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">飲食＝飯食【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0744009"><lem>飲食</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">飯食</rdg></app>美味以安身命。敷
<lb n="0744b25"/>散經典開微悅聽。食施安身。法施遷神。<note n="0744010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＝二【三】【宮】</note><note n="0744010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">一＝二【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0744010"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">二</rdg></app>
<lb n="0744b26"/>事雖快法施為最。是以比丘。念演妙法宣慧
<lb n="0744b27"/>莫癡。既自洗濯并淨塵著。如是道法永度無
<lb n="0744b28"/>窮。乃名出家具足覺了。佛說<note n="0744011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔經〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0744011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔經〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0744011"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>竟。比丘歡
<lb n="0744b29"/>喜。作禮受教</p>
